 and the dramatic growth of MBHs when normal galaxies begin to develop,\nwhich cause the memory loss of the initial conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Nov 2014 16:54:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
