tion could correctly predict\na non-vanishing reactor neutrino mixing angle and requires the Dirac phase to\nbe in the fourth quadrant, implying $\\sin\\delta $ (and $J_{CP}$) negative as\nhinted by current global analyses. Many of the analytical results presented\n(expressions for the orthogonal matrix, RH neutrino mixing matrix, masses and\nphases) can have applications beyond leptogenesis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Nov 2014 09:27:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Nov 2014 20:51:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 9 Feb 2015 17:46:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
